- RR (probability 1/4)
- RW (probability 1/4)
- WR (probability 1/4)
- WW (probability 1/4)

Since RW and WR are the same genotype, I can group them:
- RR: probability 1/4
- RW: probability 1/2 (includes both RW and WR)
- WW: probability 1/4

**Step 2: Determine which offspring have white eyes.**

